GENERAL HELP
SELL
Some shops are willing to purchase goods from their customers in order to
resell them later. If when you ~CCOMlist~CHLP the goods in a shop they say
that they will purchase things, you can ~CCOMsell~CHLP the items to the
shopkeeper for the price listed.

 ~CDEF> ~CCOMsell steel
 ~CCOMThe shopkeeper says to you~CDEF: I'll buy one ingot of steel for 5
coins.
 ~CACTThe shopkeeper buys one ingot of steel from you.

~CLABSee also: ~CREFlist, buy, currency
